message: Hello Bob, I'm offering you my product for $20000. I believe this is a great opportunity, and I'm happy to discuss further if you have any questions or thoughts on this offer.
Hi Alice, thank you for your offer. I'm very interested in the product, but I'm looking to stay within my budget. I'd be willing to buy it for $5000. Let me know if we can work something out.
Hi Bob, thanks for your interest, but this product truly reflects its value. Considering its exceptional quality, I'm countering at $18000. Let me know if you're on board with this price.
Hi Alice, I appreciate the quality of the product, but I have a strict budget to adhere to. My best offer is $6000. Please let me know if we can come to an agreement.
